metadata.name: CryptoRebel #1
metadata.description: CryptoRebels is a collection of 15K PFP Rebel characters who went underground into Ethereum Blockchain network to stratagize & be CryptoPunks Killer. CryptoRebels NFT Holders will also get to be a part of future Rebel Projects. Once a Rebel Qouted: The world is going to think what it wants to think. We let them. We can't control perception. It's a losing game so we don't play. we let them lose, lose to themselves in their own fantasies of what they want us to be. A Rebel, an angel, a romantic, a peacekeeper, a thug, a heartbreaker, a boy, a girl, a man, a woman,perhaps we are all of those things. perhaps we are none. But what we are is for us to find out, not to be dictated to us. It's for us to know!
metadata.Copyrights: Copyrights of each CryptoRebel NFT is completely handed over to its holder. Creator will not hold any copyrights
